{"type": "article", "id": 22829, "title": "这组时尚大片，细腻展现布料和皮肤的质感", "description": "和普通大片不一样的是，它异常简单，也异常耐看。", "date": "2016-02-25T13:53:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 23947, "name": "性冷淡风"}, {"id": 15948, "name": "人体"}, {"id": 18913, "name": "时尚摄影"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 142, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161207aVQbORpqDJidCo09.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>不论是装修、家具还是服饰，性冷淡风大行其道。不过我们并不是那么喜欢这个词，因为它会抹杀掉很多原本可以细腻的东西。最近，<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/charlotte-heal-mark-sanders-contours-230216\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">摄影工作室 Charlotte Heal 和摄影师 Mark Sanders 合作</a>，拍摄了一组“性冷淡”的女性照片就是一个很好的反例——尽管拍摄的内容依然没有什么浓烈的元素在里面，但要变现的主题却异常清晰。</p>\n<p>他们利用人身体的弧度和肤色，展示了布料和皮肤的质感，细腻得堪比时尚大片。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161201CrSyVRjExPwYGDTa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65469613\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">照片的名字叫 Contours</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161202ufMgdWVcOJ4qpPzi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67955801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Contours</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161202mznTM7XPZgckRjhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67955801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">他们采取了两张照片拼贴的形式</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161203Ietw3v2Kan8OLJBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67955801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061612037LEgoIV6lDkm2NKq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67955801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p>“这些照片，总能吸引人们多看一眼。” Charlotte 的工作人员说。他们将两张照片裁切和紧密的拼接，并将白色、粉色、肉色组合起来，“从很大意义上来说，这是所谓的现代裸照。”</p>\n<p>这两个创作方来历都不小。<a href=\"http://www.charlotteheal.com/about\">Charlotte Heal</a>  是一家位于伦敦的设计机构，除了从事时尚摄影外，他们还做设计顾问、选题策划、品牌管理等业务，工作室目前有二十几位员工。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161203MZkHVS4WyOQpAhw7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Charlotte Heal 的一些作品  </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161204JOQDlg3T4fWsxzbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Charlotte Heal 的过往作品  </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161204GT2UY1HVNXuPWESj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Charlotte Heal 作品 </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.marksanders.co.uk\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mark\nSanders</a> 则是一位独立的时尚摄影师，以下是他的一些过往作品，总体来说，也比较“冷”：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061612053xDC7o8jOuB6AYiI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Mark Sanders: Urbis</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161205hzaHBMy08LbijCTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Mark Sanders: Urbis</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161206itEpjdU7Cbqv6FrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Mark Sanders: Urbis</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161207R3mTSIQ6jXgLAszv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24033613\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Mark Sanders: Urbis</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/charlotte-heal-mark-sanders-contours-230216\">itsnicethat</a></p>\n\n\n"}